	   <tr><td colspan=2>I'm duel wielding Icetooth's Claws and Crystalized Sword..both 11/29. I'm doing up to 32dmg X 2 during some pulses.  Averaging around 20 with strength at 130 and hitting duel about 1/2 the time w/maxed out skill at 32. Of course the bigger hits come on lower blues, but to do up to 64 dmg per pulse is a vast immprovement over where I was without these weapons.  I'm twisting Warmth (6 dmage shield) with either Anthem and bellow to max our group offensive power or with lulliby and selos consanant chain to slow down the mob if I need to minimize damage to our group.  All depends on type of healer(s) we have in the group, and of course things change if there are multiple mobs. Net: having fun tanking doing up to 87 points in a pulse IF everything hits right.  These are the least expensive high quality weapons for bards in the game, better than Yak until 37, and probably better until 40, and much cheaper.  I got the sword for 800 and the claws for 500, about what (maybe) I could have purchased one Yak for?  But I still dream of the singing short sword.....<br><br>Valorian Quicklaw<br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
